hopobject.body: What qualifications have you got? dietbet promo code Investors have become much more wary about Canada's foreigninvestment rules after Ottawa blocked a handful of high-profiledeals, including the 2010 attempt by BHP Billiton toacquire fertilizer giant Potash Corp.
